app.component.html:
<style>
.control-section{
    margin-top: 100px;
}
</style>
<script src="script/diagram-common.ts"></script>
<style>

@font-face {
        font-family: 'e-ddb-icons';
        src: url(data:application/x-font-ttf;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('truetype');
        font-weight: normal;
        font-style: normal;
    }

    .e-ddb-icons {
        font-family: 'e-ddb-icons';
        font-size: 55px;
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: normal;
        font-variant: normal;
        text-transform: none;
        line-height: 1;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

  .e-symbolpalette {
    display: block;
  }

  .e-diagram-reset::before {
        content: "\e715";
    }
    /*To display loading sign*/
  .loading-indicator {
    border: 4px solid #f3f3f3;
    border-top: 4px solid #3498db;
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 15px;
    height: 15px;
    animation: spin 2s linear infinite;
  }
  .e-play {
        content: '\e70C';
    }
/*To display success sign*/
  .tick {
    display: none;
    animation: showTick 0.5s 0.2s forwards;
    font-size: 10px;
    width: 15px;
    height: 15px;
    padding-left: 4px;
    padding-top: 2.5px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .tick {
    background-color: green;
  }

  @keyframes spin {
    0% {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }

    100% {
      transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
  }

  @keyframes showTick {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0.5);
    }

    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }
</style>
<div class="control-section">

  <div style="width: 100%">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div style="width: 100%">
        <ejs-toolbar #toolbar id="toolbar" (clicked)="onItemClick($event)">
          <e-items>
            <e-item prefixIcon='e-play' type='Button' tooltipText='Execute' text='Execute'></e-item>
            <e-item type='Separator'></e-item>
            <e-item disabled=true prefixIcon='e-ddb-icons e-diagram-reset' type='Button' tooltipText='Reset'
              text='Reset'></e-item>

          </e-items>
        </ejs-toolbar>
        <div>
          <ejs-diagram #diagram id="diagram" width="100%" height="645px" [tool]="diagramtool"
            [constraints]="diagramConstraints" [getNodeDefaults]="getNodeDefaults"
            [getConnectorDefaults]="getConnectorDefaults" (created)="created()" [snapSettings]="snapSettings">
            <e-nodes>
              <e-node id="newTravelRequestRecieved" [offsetX]="100" [offsetY]="245" [width]="60" [height]="60"
                [shape]="start" [addInfo]="start">
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="getTravelRequestDetails" [offsetX]="250" [offsetY]="245" [width]="100" [height]="80"
                [shape]="taskShape">
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="getRequesterProfile" [offsetX]="400" [offsetY]="245" [width]="100" [height]="80"
                [shape]="taskShape">
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="getManagerDetails" [offsetX]="550" [offsetY]="245" [width]="100" [height]="80"
                [shape]="taskShape">
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="setStatusAsRejected" [offsetX]="700" [offsetY]="245" [width]="100" [height]="80"
                [shape]="taskShape">
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="setStatusAsAccepted" [offsetX]="850" [offsetY]="245" [width]="100" [height]="80"
                [shape]="taskShape">
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="setNextApprovalStatusAsRejected" [offsetX]="1100" [offsetY]="245" [width]="100" [height]="80"
                [shape]="taskShape">
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="setNextApprovalStatusAsAccepted" [offsetX]="1250" [offsetY]="245" [width]="100" [height]="80"
                [shape]="taskShape">
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="initiateApprovalWithManager" [offsetX]="550" [offsetY]="445" [width]="100" [height]="80"
                [shape]="taskShape">
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="checkApprovalStatus" [offsetX]="700" [offsetY]="445" [width]="100" [height]="80"
                [shape]="gateWay">
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="checkIfItIsAnInternaltionalTravel" [offsetX]="850" [offsetY]="445" [width]="100" [height]="80"
                [shape]="gateWay">
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="initialteApprovalWithNextLevelManager" [offsetX]="1000" [offsetY]="445" [width]="100"
                [height]="80" [shape]="taskShape" >
              </e-node>
              <e-node id="checkLevel2-ApprovalStatus" [offsetX]="1130" [offsetY]="445" [width]="100" [height]="80"
                [shape]="gateWay" >
              </e-node>
            </e-nodes>
            <e-connectors>
              <e-connector id="newTravelRequestRecieved-getTravelRequestDetails" sourceID="newTravelRequestRecieved"
                targetID="getTravelRequestDetails" [addInfo]="firstLevel">
              </e-connector>

              <e-connector id="getTravelRequestDetails-getRequesterProfile" sourceID="getTravelRequestDetails"
                targetID="getRequesterProfile" [addInfo]="secondLevel">
              </e-connector>

              <e-connector id="getRequesterProfile-getManagerDetails" sourceID="getRequesterProfile"
                targetID="getManagerDetails" [addInfo]="thirdLevel">
              </e-connector>

              <e-connector id="getManagerDetails-initiateApprovalWithManager" sourceID="getManagerDetails"
                targetID="initiateApprovalWithManager" [addInfo]="fourthLevel">
              </e-connector>

              <e-connector id="initiateApprovalWithManager-checkApprovalStatus" sourceID="initiateApprovalWithManager"
                targetID="checkApprovalStatus" [addInfo]="fifthLevel">
              </e-connector>
              <e-connector id="checkApprovalStatus-setStatusAsRejected" sourceID="checkApprovalStatus"
                targetID="setStatusAsRejected" [addInfo]="sixthLevel">
                <e-connector-annotations>
                  <e-connector-annotation content="Rejected" [offset]="conOffset" [style]="connAnnotStyle">
                  </e-connector-annotation>
                </e-connector-annotations>
              </e-connector>

              <e-connector id="checkApprovalStatus-checkIfItIsAnInternaltionalTravel" sourceID="checkApprovalStatus"
                targetID="checkIfItIsAnInternaltionalTravel" [addInfo]="seventhLevel">
                <e-connector-annotations>
                  <e-connector-annotation content="Accepted" [style]="connAnnotStyle">
                  </e-connector-annotation>
                </e-connector-annotations>
              </e-connector>

              <e-connector id="checkIfItIsAnInternaltionalTravel-setStatusAsAccepted"
                sourceID="checkIfItIsAnInternaltionalTravel" targetID="setStatusAsAccepted" [addInfo]="eighthLevel">
                <e-connector-annotations>
                  <e-connector-annotation content="No" [offset]="conOffset" [style]="connAnnotStyle">
                  </e-connector-annotation>
                </e-connector-annotations>
              </e-connector>

              <e-connector id="checkIfItIsAnInternaltionalTravel-initialteApprovalWithNextLevelManager"
                sourceID="checkIfItIsAnInternaltionalTravel" targetID="initialteApprovalWithNextLevelManager"
                [addInfo]="ninethLevel">
                <e-connector-annotations>
                  <e-connector-annotation content="Yes" [style]="connAnnotStyle">
                  </e-connector-annotation>
                </e-connector-annotations>
              </e-connector>

              <e-connector id="initialteApprovalWithNextLevelManager-checkLevel2-ApprovalStatus"
                sourceID="initialteApprovalWithNextLevelManager" targetID="checkLevel2-ApprovalStatus"
                [addInfo]="tenthLevel">
              </e-connector>

              <e-connector id="checkLevel2-ApprovalStatus-setNextApprovalStatusAsRejected"
                sourceID="checkLevel2-ApprovalStatus" targetID="setNextApprovalStatusAsRejected"
                [addInfo]="eleventhLevel">
                <e-connector-annotations>
                  <e-connector-annotation content="Rejected" [offset]="conOffset" [style]="connAnnotStyle">
                  </e-connector-annotation>
                </e-connector-annotations>
              </e-connector>

              <e-connector id="checkLevel2-ApprovalStatus-setNextApprovalStatusAsAccepted"
                sourceID="checkLevel2-ApprovalStatus" sourcePortID="right_port"
                targetID="setNextApprovalStatusAsAccepted" [addInfo]="twelthLevel">
                <e-connector-annotations>
                  <e-connector-annotation content="Accepted" [offset]="conOffset" [style]="connAnnotStyle">
                  </e-connector-annotation>
                </e-connector-annotations>
              </e-connector>
            </e-connectors>
          </ejs-diagram>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
